namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::Sprite::pivotJoint

\brief join sprites together at a particular location in layer coordinates (*Chipmunk Physics Only*)

If a breaking force is given, then the joint will break, generating a SpriteBreakEvent, if greater than that amount of force is applied to the joint.

\returns the cpConstraint for the Joint in case you want to do anything special with it

**/ }